  "title": "Abstract Spawn Eggs",
  "description": "Tweaks the new Spawn Egg textures to be more abstract (and consistent)",
  "body": "### ⚠️⚠️⚠️The resource pack is still not finished and very much WIP. All spawn eggs' textures aren't completed yet. Thank you for your patience and understanding. \n#\n\n# Abstract Spawn Eggs🥚\n## What does it do?🐣\nThe new vanilla spawn eggs are quite cool, but they dont really make sense. Abstract Spawn Eggs retextures the new spawn egg textures to be more abstract, that is make them less \"look like the literal mob in egg shape\" and more \"capturing the important visuals to kinda make sense in the form of an egg\". It also changes the size, and even color and shape, of some eggs to better represent the mob that it spawns and removes the water that aquatic mob spawn eggs are in. Some vanilla spawn eggs, for some reason, doesn't match the others' \"look like the literal mob in egg shape\" and are already quite abstract, so I consider some eggs to not need a retexture, such as the Phantom spawn egg and the Drowned spawn egg. Abstract Spawn Eggs strives to be as vanilla-like as possible. \n\n\n## List of Spawn Egg Progress🚡\n26 out of 83 spawn eggs are ready. In the following table you can see which spawn egg retextures are...\n\n|||\n|:-:|:-|\n|✅️|...finished|\n|❎️|...not needed|\n|❌️|...incomplete|\n\n|Spawn Egg|Status|Vanilla|Retexture|\n|:-|:-:|:-:|:-:|\n|Allay|❌️|<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/0515c5e808faccd5e69a2d8ae53bbc0a0f31c0d2.png\" style=\"image-rendering: pixelated;\" alt=\"Vanilla Allay but no interpolation\">||\n|Armadillo|❌️|<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/001f2f601a949bed9102193189562db0d414481b.png\" style=\"image-rendering: pixelated;\" alt=\"Vanilla Armadillo\">||\n|Axolotl|❌️|<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8b45a2e43d7ae8f02f015911ae0fe01f1db1771b.png\" style=\"image-rendering: pixelated;\" alt=\"Vanilla Axolotl\">||\n|Bat|❌️|<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/2cfb90081c81da7ecd2d1da81dca00a5254dc3d5.png\" style=\"image-rendering: pixelated;\" a